Package: surveySHAP
Type: Package
Title: SHAP-Based Interpretation Tools for Survey Models
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jingtian", "Yu",
           email = "your_email@domain.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for fitting and interpreting four survey-model backends:
    linear regression, binomial generalized linear models, numeric xgboost,
    and logistic xgboost. The package provides explicit SHAP calculations for
    lm/glm, native TreeSHAP for xgboost, weighted group-level summaries, and
    bootstrap utilities.
